      • isShareLocked

        boolean isShareLocked()
        Query if screen share is locked by host.

      • lockShare

        MobileRTCSDKError lockShare(boolean isLock)
        The host/co-host can use this function to lock current meeting share.
        Parameters:
        isLock - TRUE means to lock the meeting share, FALSE not.
        Returns:
        If the function succeeds, the return value is SDKErr_Success. Otherwise failed, for more details, see MobileRTCSDKError. *Note* Once the meeting is locked by the host/co-host, other user can not share except the host/co-host.
